\b0\fs24 \cf0 Deploy your mining probes as you prospect for ores on floating planetoids. Build mining bases to extract resources and increase your power. But beware of competing factions encroaching on your territory! Defend your claims with all the technology at your disposal. Attack your enemies with various weaponry that reacts with real Newtonian motion.\
