\b0\fs48 \
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li360\fi360\sl288\slmult1\pardirnatural

\fs24 \cf0 The goal is to control all the planetoids in the play region and destroy all the enemy factions.  Players will need to deploy mining bases to extract ores, send out probes to prospect for needed resources, build defenses and attack other players bases and weapons.\
The game strategy will involve building defensible networks of planetoids that can extract resources with their mines and build armaments to defend and attack other players as conflicts arise.  Tactics will need to take into account the Newtonian behaviors of the planetoids and projectiles.  Orbiting, gravity wells, and slingshotting will needed to be mastered to tactical advantage.\
The game should work over a network (2-8 players?) with a turn-based timeline. \
